OL,3,GNEWSCSTV presses ahead with Glasgow
OL,4,Cpresentation for 6pm programme
OL,5,
OL,6,FSTV unexpectedly tried out the new
OL,7,Fset-up for its 6pm news programme
OL,8,Ftonight.
OL,10,FViewers in both the STV Central and STV
OL,11,FNorth regions saw a programme presented
OL,12,Ffrom Glasgow.
OL,14,FIt was presented by Andrea Brymer, one
OL,15,Fof STV North's anchors.
OL,17,FThe content was the same, except for a
OL,18,Fsection in the middle devoted to
OL,19,Fregional stories. There were also
OL,20,Fseparate weather forecasts.
OL,23,EPub: 09-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
