OL,3,GNEWSCSTV presses ahead with Glasgow
OL,4,Cpresentation for 6pm programme
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt is our understanding that there will
OL,7,Fbe a separate programme again on
OL,8,FFriday.
OL,10,FBoth of tonight's programmes can be
OL,11,Fseen on the STV Player.
OL,13,FIt is unclear whether tonight's format
OL,14,Fwill be used every night from next
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,FOfcom says the minimum amount of
OL,18,Fcontent specifically for each region
OL,19,Fcan be averaged across the year.
OL,21,FThe new combined programme is thought
OL,22,Fto be starting properly on Monday.
OL,23,EPub: 09-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
